@startuml
title SequenceDiagram

actor User
participant "UI" as UI
participant "TransactionController" as TC
participant "AccountService" as AS
participant "Database" as DB

User -> UI: Добавить новую транзакцию
UI -> TC: createTransaction(amount, category, date)
TC -> AS: validateAccountBalance(accountId, amount)
AS -> DB: SELECT balance FROM accounts
DB --> AS: баланс счета
AS --> TC: результат проверки
TC -> DB: INSERT INTO transactions
DB --> TC: ID новой транзакции
TC -> AS: updateAccountBalance(accountId, amount)
AS -> DB: UPDATE accounts SET balance
DB --> AS: подтверждение
AS --> TC: обновленный баланс
TC --> UI: транзакция успешно создана
UI --> User: отображение результата
@enduml